004package test;
005
006import java.util.ArrayList;
007import java.io.FileOutputStream;
008import mkt.Models;
009import mkt.Model;
010import mkt.Quotes;
011import kut.*;
012import extDb.QuotesDb;
013import data.SimParams;
014
015/** Test references. */
016public class J04refs {
017  /**
018  Run test.
019  @param rq Request.
020  @return <pre>
021    {}
022    </pre>
023  */
024  public static Dic<String> run (Dic<String> rq) {
025    String jf = Js.rs(rq.get("jf"));
026    Quotes qts = QuotesDb.read();
027    double[][] cls = qts.closes;
028    ArrayList<Model> list = Models.list();
029    Arr.sort(list, (m1, m2) ->
030      m1.id.compareTo(m2.id) < 0);
031
032    FileOutputStream f = File.wopen(jf);
033    for (Model md : list) {
034      String mdId = md.id;
035      double[] params = SimParams.paramBases(mdId);
036      String rfs = Js.w(Arr.map(
037        Arr.mk(md.calc.apply(cls, params)),
038        (rs) -> Js.w(Arr.map(Arr.mk(rs), (n) -> Js.w(n)))
039      ));
040      File.writeText(f, mdId + ":" + rfs + "\n");
041    }
042    File.close(f);
043
044    return Dic.mk();
045  }
046
047}
